name: WorldSurf
body:
### what are these? These are a few navigation tests for a mobile and tablet UI design. The design is for WorldSurf, a beach information application. The tests were conducted to fine tune placement of UI elements, and done on [Usability Hub](http://usabilityhub.com/). ### Mobile [Mobile Signup Test](https://usabilityhub.com/tests/e1224497a3d5/results/e9a1a648d25c)
[Mobile Signup Test continued](https://usabilityhub.com/tests/cd4042febde8/results/2d5f2080796e)
[Mobile Selected Beach Page Test](https://usabilityhub.com/tests/c7bbfecf3cf5/results/a784f38a6f84)
[Mobile Login Test](https://usabilityhub.com/tests/2ff58de642c5/results/f09a957e6188)
[Mobile Search Test](https://usabilityhub.com/tests/54a6bc33be31/results/d1884b473031) ### Tablet [Tablet Login Test](https://usabilityhub.com/tests/d40e0be8bd10/results/d62faf4e1317)
[Tablet Bookmarks Test](https://usabilityhub.com/tests/273d86006b55/results/fb41f59e11f4)
[Tablet Bookmark Test](https://usabilityhub.com/tests/c3085dbed945/results/326ebd7e5b6a)
